        <p>I'm a software engineering student and AI solutions engineer based in Draper, UT — building systems that work in production, not just in demos.</p>
        <p>My work lives at the intersection of <strong>LLM engineering, Python automation, and hardware-level systems</strong>. Two-agent CrewAI pipelines, firmware patches for drone autopilots, ML inference pipelines from sensor to prediction — I care about the full stack.</p>
        <p>Completing a BS in Software Engineering at Ensign College. Currently at <strong>Utah Community Credit Union</strong> as a technical analyst. Led 16-person team in Chicago — <strong>cut cost-per-conversion 25%, +35% engagement</strong>.</p>
        <p>Bilingual in <strong>Spanish</strong>. First-principles thinker.</p>
